  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13095223/ski-holidays.jpg" alt="skihero" data-udi="umb://media/91495348444a48e0a4ee10f2a82b2f2c" /></p>
<h2><strong>We don't just take you on a ski holiday, we make your ski holiday.</strong></h2>
<p>When you choose a ski holiday with Inghams, every detail and every interaction is built on over 85 years of passion and experience. We’ve spent these years building lasting relationships with hoteliers, airlines and in resort suppliers to ensure we can offer the best ski holiday and recommendations. Curated and elevated just for you.</p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>✔️ Huge choice of resorts and airports</h3>
<ul>
<li>75 resorts across 7 countries in Europe and Canada.</li>
<li>Your choice of 17 local airports to fly from.</li>
<li>Chalets, self-catered apartments and 3-5* hotels. </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>✔️ With you all the way</h3>
<ul>
<li>Before and after your holiday, our reservations and guest relations team are on hand. </li>
<li>You'll have the reassurance of our reps, when in resort.</li>
<li>Flights, transfers and accommodation are included. </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>✔️ You're In Safe Hands</h3>
<ul>
<li>Flexibility to move your holiday to a later date, up to the point that your full balance is due, with no admin fee from us.<span style="font-weight: 400;"><br /></span></li>
<li>Our holidays are ABTA/ATOL protected and with over 85 years of experience, you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday. </li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<p><a name="competition"></a></p>
<h2>Extra special ski holidays</h2>
<p>Chemmy Alcott, Winter Olympian and Tim Warwood, professional Snowboarder, got together to talk about what makes their skiing and snowboarding holidays with us extra special:</p>
<p><iframe width="100%" height="450" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IA2Ixv-dvMg" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Get inspired for your next ski holiday</h2>
<p>We want to make your ski holiday feel perfect for you. Whether you’re a thrill seeker hunting down the best off-piste, a relaxed skier who enjoys those cruisy blues, a mountain lover looking for the best views or maybe you’re looking for something extra special this year. We've hand selected our top resorts and accommodations, that will make your ski holiday.</p>
<div class="g6">
<p><img src="/media/13092559/masthead_thrilling-image-501x300-2.jpg" alt="Thrilling ski holidays" data-udi="umb://media/67617e750710454e8cadae118fec20fd" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/187ad54f003345babb272c88c46d9bc0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/187ad54f003345babb272c88c46d9bc0}" title="Thrilling"><strong>Thrilling</strong></a></h3>
<p>Think challenging Olympic level black runs, heli-skiing and off-piste opportunities, all just a hop skip and a jump to town centres, main lifts and legendary nightlife.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<p><img src="/media/13092558/masthead_relaxing-image-501x300.jpg" alt="Relaxing ski holidays" data-udi="umb://media/16b9b894063645cfbd94abb06b4f9945" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/ec918737d8c1420b85ac1a8e4f626ac3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ec918737d8c1420b85ac1a8e4f626ac3}" title="Relaxing"><strong>Relaxing</strong></a></h3>
<p>Gentle cruisy blue runs on bluebird days, the best spots for slow mountain lunches and coffee stops, with a little bit extra relaxation with walking and spas at the bottom of the slopes.</p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<p><img src="/media/13092560/breathtaking-501x300.jpg" alt="Breathtaking ski holidays" data-udi="umb://media/a35a1a36c5094589a60a772c1f801307" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a66cd1f874ff493ebee56b2a14c93214" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a66cd1f874ff493ebee56b2a14c93214}" title="Breathtaking"><strong>Breathtaking</strong></a></h3>
<p>For those who love everything about the mountains - whether that’s waking up to majestic views of snowy landscapes or enjoying lunch with 360 degree views.  </p>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<p><img src="/media/13092561/masthead_amazing-image-501x300.jpg" alt="Amazing ski holidays" data-udi="umb://media/b5fd0c6ccffc44548a56bb9aadd02b46" /></p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/42a6af07522140609a34e2bac1cbf9e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/42a6af07522140609a34e2bac1cbf9e5}" title="Amazing"><strong>Amazing</strong></a></h3>
<p>For the ones looking for something a little bit different than the norm - we’ve got castles, luxury spa hotels and resorts that offer Michelin star restaurants as well as great ski runs.</p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div>
<h3>Discover how Inghams can make your ski holiday: </h3>
<p>Answer a small set of questions so we can help narrow down your holiday search. <a data-udi="umb://document/bfd20e6bb3b1432a89d67d6847c14332" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfd20e6bb3b1432a89d67d6847c14332}" title="Take our Quiz">Start Quiz &gt;&gt;</a> </p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Looking for great value?</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Explore our handpicked selection of top resorts and hotels that allow you to get the most of your ski holiday this Winter. </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b7e31f4645514434bec76a3728e974c0}" title="Serre Chevalier">Serre Chevalier - France</a></h3>
<p>This often overlooked friendly resort offers great value with over 250km of well-connected tree lines pistes to explore. It's also known as being one of the sunniest French resorts with a picturesque town. </p>
<p><img src="/media/13092619/serre-chevalier-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/bb966c67477e47828e8d43a1c742e121" /></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Hotels we recommend: </span></p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/35e01a42a9a94f2f98a2de0f27a4ba32" href="/{localLink:umb://document/35e01a42a9a94f2f98a2de0f27a4ba32}" title="Parc Hotel and Spa">Parc Hotel and Spa - 4*</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/a4ebbcede44f4673bff372e1584edefd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4ebbcede44f4673bff372e1584edefd}" title="Hotel Plein Sud">Hotel Plein Sud - 3*</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e86e0f4a587e4cd8be3c24d7da459a59}" title="Pas de la Casa">Pas de la Casa - Andorra</a></h3>
<p>The highest of the Andorran resorts with slopes up to 2,640m, Pas de la Casa sits close to the French border. You'll find prices in resort often cheaper than ski resorts in neighbouring countries. </p>
<p><img src="/media/13092617/andorra-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/d523e79b464c4304afde9b721c40a641" /></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Hotels we recommend:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/ee2b67dab18341aba9a31ae2ed8834ea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee2b67dab18341aba9a31ae2ed8834ea}" title="Hotel Font D’Argent">Hotel Font d'Argent - 4*</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/a4e20608b1604de3a86296784bdb45af" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4e20608b1604de3a86296784bdb45af}" title="Hotel Magic">Hotel Magic - 4*</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4"></div>
<div class="g4"></div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia - Italy</a></h3>
<p>From Cervinia you can enjoy incredible views and skiing in both Italy and Switzerland with a combined ski area. Ski over to Zermatt, famous for the iconic Matterhorn, but enjoy better value staying on the Italian side. </p>
<p><img src="/media/13092618/cervinia-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a6aefdb1d061493585cd7b8a47a79fff" /></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Hotels we recommend:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/5ae51238e1cc4964a3b8aed127ed4af8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5ae51238e1cc4964a3b8aed127ed4af8}" title="Hotel Punta Maquignaz">Hotel Punta Maquignaz - 4*</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/dfd445f3f5c4470394ae124d06dd4ece" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dfd445f3f5c4470394ae124d06dd4ece}" title="Hotel Serenella">Hotel Serenella - 3*</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/bf821de09e4545d997e23a8ff6ae540a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bf821de09e4545d997e23a8ff6ae540a}" class="c-btn">View best value deals</a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</span></p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>]]></bodyText>
